cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with semantic segmentation in adverse weather conditions, which is a common problem in the field of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also proposes the use of neural networks for sensor data fusion, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper introduces a new training method for neural networks, which is related to the field of neural networks (cs.NE).
